{"tid":1917416,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<歐洲中國> 義大利封城消息走漏！　上萬民眾出逃米蘭","createTime":"2020-03-09T13:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T13:29:40.000Z","uid":227801,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2c41466c629e4ae05a3bcb55ad8ae6e3c666d9b1","tid":1917416,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200309/1662986.htm#ixzz6GCFJRcnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200309%2F1662986.htm%23ixzz6GCFJRcnY&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM6g2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=b9fc3a38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200309/1662986.htm#ixzz6GCFJRcnY</a><br />\n實習記者陳妙津／綜合報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FIMTip4xZws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFIMTip4xZws&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM6g2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=797d83cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FIMTip4xZws</a><br />\n義大利北部新冠肺炎疫情惡化，總理孔蒂8日凌晨表示，他已簽署封城禁令，宣布即日起封閉倫巴底、威尼托等經濟大區，至少隔離到4月3日，其中包含米蘭等知名大城，數以萬計的民眾得知消息後緊急星夜出門，前往火車站搭車逃離疫區，街頭一時間滿是逃亡潮宛如喪屍出巡，出城道路上也大塞車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4744/d4744536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4744%2Fd4744536.jpg&h=eaf82577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《衛報》報導，包括金融大都米蘭在內，整個倫巴底大區及疫情最嚴重的北義14省將在即日起封閉，至少到4月3日才會再度開放，這是由於義大利死亡人數一天大增133人，確診人數暴增1492例而採取的緊急措施，目前義大利已成為中國外，疫情最嚴重的國家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4744/d4744535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4744%2Fd4744535.jpg&h=64772294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民眾在該段期間不得隨意出入，婚喪喜慶等聚會活動，電影院、酒吧等人群聚集地都強制取消並關閉至4月3日。當局表示，只要有民眾不遵守禁令，將會面臨3個月的徒刑，以及206歐元的罰金。總理孔蒂表示，「我們瞭解禁令會為群眾帶來不便和犧牲，但這次我們必須負起責任，我們必須明白，所有人都要遵循這些措施。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4744/d4744534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4744%2Fd4744534.jpg&h=a8dd220a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過封城消息提早被當地晚報走漏風聲，導致數以萬計的民眾接獲消息後，提著大包小包匆忙趕往米蘭車站，期望能趕上最後一班通宵列車出城。從車站大廳向下望去，能見到民眾密密麻麻地擠在通道上，朝著同一方向匆忙離去，宛如喪屍出巡。<br />\n<br />\n病毒學教授羅伯托（Roberto Burioni）則警告，「新聞洩漏禁令讓許多人趁此機會逃離，會使禁令出現相反效果，有些逃離者甚至會因此在離城過程中受到感染」"},{"pid":"cdbb6734ead137b48f5e3eae1ad4be6d7dadd4ed","tid":1917416,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"昨日支那 今日EU"},{"pid":"b1737150e7e1fe8162e48bf19696eb70f17580db","tid":1917416,"uid":27946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"武漢2.0"},{"pid":"800259b26a20ecf002a32a58080e9e301d6c9912","tid":1917416,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"封城消息走漏呢個放係任何國家都一定會發生<br />\n<br />\n因為政府內部一定有親人係當地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e653dd6d2e7c050a984795fc6873b88831da3e13","tid":1917416,"uid":166982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"西方嘅東亞病夫"},{"pid":"0961aed1785f7aa1f16e5f0ecb1517e889803b25","tid":1917416,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"武漢翻版<br />\n<br />\n全歐洲通輯倫巴第人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c958bf2f8697091c49ca97b1d989433c484fccf","tid":1917416,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"原來支那人世界皆是啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4310c0986a3d40ac1a062c168cc35f1b6a9854","tid":1917416,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:15:16.00